Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And as always, we will keep working on our same project.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is how we left it
